cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use MedScale in academic work, please cite it as below."
title: "MedScale: An open research platform for verifiable clinical AI"
abstract: >-
  MedScale is an open-source research platform for verifiable clinical AI: FHIR-native,
  grammar-constrained, validator-grounded, deterministically benchmarked, and fully
  reproducible. It is trained and evaluated on synthetic data only.
type: software
authors:
